Frank Edwin Wright III -LRB- born December 9 , 1972 -RRB- , known professionally as Tr√© Cool , is a German-born American musician , drummer and composer , best known as the drummer for the punk rock band Green Day .
He replaced the band 's former drummer , John Kiffmeyer , in 1990 as Kiffmeyer felt that he should spend more time towards college .
Cool has also played in The Lookouts , Samiam and the Green Day side-projects The Network and the Foxboro Hot Tubs .